**Subagent Spawn Flow:**

```typescript
// 1. Parent agent decides to spawn (via LLM tool call)
const subagentRegistry = getSubagentRegistry();
const childSession = await subagentRegistry.spawn({
  agentId: "researcher",
  config: {
    model: "claude-haiku",           // Different model
    workspace: "/tmp/research-" + id,
    skills: ["web_search", "read_file"],
  },
  parentSessionKey: parentKey,
});

// 2. Registry validates
if (getCurrentDepth(parentKey) >= maxDepth) {
  throw new Error("Max subagent depth exceeded");
}

// 3. Create session key
const childKey = `agent:researcher:${generateId()}`;

// 4. Prepare context (copy from parent)
await contextEngine.prepareSubagentSpawn({
  parentSessionKey,
  childSessionKey,
});

// 5. Dispatch to subagent lane
await dispatchToLane({
  lane: CommandLane.Subagent,
  sessionKey: childKey,
  content: {
    type: "subagent_spawn",
    config: childConfig,
  },
});

// 6. Send task
await sendToSession(childKey, {
  role: "user",
  content: "Research latest AI trends...",
});

// 7. Wait for completion (with timeout)
const result = await subagentRegistry.waitForCompletion(childKey, {
  timeout: 5 * 60 * 1000, // 5 minutes
});

// 8. Use result in parent
```

**ACP Protocol (Agent Communication Protocol):**

Subagents communicate via WebSocket using ACP:

```typescript
// Parent sends to child
ws.send(JSON.stringify({
  type: "message",
  sessionKey: childKey,
  content: { role: "user", text: "Do research..." },
}));

// Child replies
ws.send(JSON.stringify({
  type: "announce",
  sessionKey: parentKey,
  content: {
    type: "subagent_result",
    result: { findings: "..." },
  },
}));
```

**Use Cases:**

| Use Case | Child Agent Config | Parent Benefit |
|----------|-------------------|----------------|
| Parallel research | Multiple subagents, each search different source | Reduce total time by 70% |
| Specialized tasks | Child with coding-agent skills | Parent doesn't need those skills |
| Cost optimization | Child uses cheaper model (Haiku vs Sonnet) | Save 80% cost on simple tasks |
| Isolation | Child in container sandbox | Security boundary |

